high_descs: Turn left and walk past the sofa and countertop, to the fridge on your right
Get the mug out of the fridge
Put the mug into the microwave, heat it, and get the mug out of the microwave
Turn right and walk ahead towards the bedroom, then hang a right and head towards the desk, and go to the shelf on your right
Put the mug in the shelf
Walk few steps front then turn left and walk straight to reach the fridge
Open the fridge and take a mug from it and close the door
Turn towards back and reach the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the mug into the oven and close it. After few seconds, open the door and take the mug out and again close the oven.
Turn right and walk straight and enter into the opposite side room and turn right to reach the shelf
Put the mug on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the mug on the shelf

high_descs: Turn around and go near the fridge
Take the mug from the fridge
Turn around and go near the microwave
Put the mug into the microwave
Take it out and go near the shelf
Put the mug on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Placed the mug on the shelf
